public class TransposedUpdateablePreferenceData<I,​U>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FastUpdateablePreferenceData<I,​U>, org.ranksys.fast.preference.FastPointWisePreferenceData<I,​U>
Updateable transposed preferences, where users and items change roles. This class is useful to simplify the implementation of many algorithms that work user or item-wise, such as similarities or matrix factorization.
Author:
Javier Sanz-Cruzado (javier.sanz-cruzado@uam.es), SaÃºl Vargas (saul.vargas@uam.es)
